title: ManTrendster UZeited 8/11: Merrick Garland, MSNBC, Bill Russell, Beto O'Rourke, Brittney Griner, Games
itunes:title: ManTrendster UZeited 8/11: Merrick Garland, MSNBC, Bill Russell, Beto O'Rourke, Brittney Griner, Games
description:
In this edition of ManTrendster UZeited, Miles and DJ Danl discuss Merrick Garland unsealing the Trump search warrant, MSNBC caping for Trump?, the NBA retiring Bill Russell's number league-wide, Beto O'Rourke clapping back at a cackling heckler, the Brittney Griner prisoner swap talks, and their first, last, best and worst games!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
